"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"It is difficult for people without ideas to achieve success. At present, the population of PC Internet + mobile Internet in China has reached 850 million people. Any small branch contains huge business opportunities. A Didi Taxi started from 800,000 two years ago, and now has 15 billion in cash on hand. To put it simply, it is to achieve the ultimate in a taxi-hailing software. In China, such opportunities will appear in various fields in the next 10 years.\\n\\n```\\nWhen we choose a subdivision of an industry, we have to think, I want to thoroughly understand this point, and go to the whole country, to reach tens of billions. After having this ideal, we started with one detail, and achieved the ultimate in this detail, and achieved the whole country. You have to make money on a key issue before thinking about expansion. Don't do many functions and many services as soon as you go up. If the front is too long, people's energy will not keep up, and it will be difficult to do it.\\n\\nWe must choose a specific point and do our best to make this point the ultimate. After occupying the national market, think about expansion. For example, after Didi Dache occupied the entire taxi market, it expanded to the agent driving business. Eat up this piece of fat in the driving market. After Didi has eaten the fat of the driver, can he continue to eat the market of the driving school? Can it eat up the used car market? They are all around the car market to eat, eating deep and wide, I think a 100 billion-level enterprise will be born easily.\\n\\nIn the Internet industry, there are really many opportunities. Moreover, it is extremely easy to turn a dick into a wealthy industry. Those who want to develop their careers in this industry should have more contact with people in this industry and enter the circle of this industry to discuss, explore, and learn. What kind of people you discuss, explore, and study with now determine the career you will engage in three to five years from now. It is basically impossible to achieve a career quickly and to explore completely on your own. It is necessary to learn to learn from the thinking and practices of outstanding people in the industry. Then go to practice and become your own thinking and practice.\\n```\",\"timestamp\":1634804760,\"title\":\"Internet entrepreneurship must have big ideas and small practices.\"},\"digest\":\"zNfeu4llP-tbfGhiCoC9LOTx4_5cpeInyComzaBKsgg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0B27cE1053585ef548Cd78618Ee0b73D84246712\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FWHKuUadZNUD2AcIaH2jGL63PlPKxJxdB2P-UVSGKyo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"TGI_NAnOwHtvZb-9m7wqNj24YxnrIjurKisiIm7dHV0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"epaErovB5zVb4F3s9ZIaESoVlXvWXseYdCCBYf9tVDNJ30jSLfvyVNEa2bikgm3o9gICAwTtvOOkpPF14tRJyA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9d86f85b2660a8cb6873525924f9adb0c5f51dfb6229fed7a757ade2793c2f19347cb8076af39b12116743e30b34d1bacb42c80a0030cd272dd62c1ad0ad21081b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FWHKuUadZNUD2AcIaH2jGL63PlPKxJxdB2P-UVSGKyo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"TGI_NAnOwHtvZb-9m7wqNj24YxnrIjurKisiIm7dHV0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"zNfeu4llP-tbfGhiCoC9LOTx4_5cpeInyComzaBKsgg\"}"